{"tid":952900,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE作文題目求評","createTime":"2018-12-23T13:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T05:47:51.000Z","uid":227929,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"199795ddd55f453f8f4aef020940588a2dd09f0d","tid":952900,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"題目:The joys of being a teenager in Hong Kong<br />\n中四水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以講埋大概lv幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGood morning everyone, I am Chris Wong and I&lsquo;m a Form Four student from LIHKG Secondary School.I am glad that i have a chance to share the topic,the joys of being a teenager in Hong Kong, to all of you. As a Hong Kong teenager.Most of us think Hong Kong is a city without hope and future.As there is impossible for buy a house and everything is expensive.But let me tell you.You are wrong and the future of the city is on your hands.<br />\n <br />\nAlthough the most vibrant time of Hong Kong has been past.But Hong Kong is still 6th safest city in the world.In 2018 there is only about 7500 violent crime happened in Hong Kong.Compared to New York city there had about 96000 violent crime happened in 2017.Because of the Hong Kong Police Forces provide a low crime rate so that we can have a great environment for our healthy growth.<br />\n <br />\nFrom 2009 the Government of Hong Kong has started provide twelve years' free to all children attending public sector schools.Unlike the teenager in those developing country.Every Hong Kong teenager have the chance to study.Although some student is poor.They can improve their life through studying.And now the Education Bureau has started to promote the STEM Education.To let the students learn and skim more about Science.<br />\n <br />\nWith the Basic Law we can have freedom of speech,publication association,assembly,procession and demonstration.Therefore Hong Kong teenagers, can express our opinions and are able to take part in some political movements. Not only adults but also teenagers can voice their own opinions related to policies.<br />\n <br />\nI firmly believe that there are a lots of joys in Hong Kong waiting for all of you to feel.  Stay optimistic and you can find countless joys being a teenager in this city.  Thank you"},{"pid":"75f4c53791721afd6070ef27be7599dd07b5d478","tid":952900,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a6878e725e0bd3f4ed0266ce3c35c1b8127c59f","tid":952900,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75f4c53791721afd6070ef27be7599dd07b5d478","tid":952900,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T13:58:54.000Z","msg":"你講得啱<br />\nthx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c282c111bed851b674911c202ec523215ba34902","tid":952900,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"Lv2"},{"pid":"fe2776fce292bf03b869242aba381ab4e845208e","tid":952900,"uid":223757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf9c2c9fb32318010a9dd365f9c6e32826c1ef6f","tid":952900,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:25:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8523542da501b006e039f705ef2176196ad374ce","tid":952900,"uid":135182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:27:26.000Z","msg":"你將成篇嘢過一次grammarly先會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44501712c8220d8525671040bbea52dd2788bf96","tid":952900,"uid":9028,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"cit